SendPayTx
====

Goal

	Account A send 1TAKA to "80ba149c1e71ca4576198998418bc47d4e297ab2"

Account A

	{
        "MinPrivkey": "",
        "privkey": "",
        "pubkey": "",
        "address": "4881992453ee79525619c9fc212b68b69db069cd",
        "txids": {
                "pay": {
                        "txs": [],
                        "MerkleRoot": ""
                }
        },
        "balance": 0
	}


# Using console
### Node Start.

	node init.js

### And type to console.

	node console.js sendpaytx  80ba149c1e71ca4576198998418bc47d4e297ab2 1

Check with [explorer](https://neko.taka.site/explorer) if it is sent properly.



# Using library

### load library.

	<script src="https://neko.taka.site/lib/TAKALibRapper"></script>

### Using function.

	const TAKAFUNCTIONS = new TAKA.RappingFunctions("https://neko.taka.site");
	let txid = await TAKAFUNCTIONS.SendTransaction("",1,"pay","80ba149c1e71ca4576198998418bc47d4e297ab2",1,"");
	console.log(txid);

* let txid = await TAKAFUNCTIONS.SendTransaction(key,type,tag,toaddress,amount,data);
